    <Authors>Armando Fernandez (DevMando)</Authors>
    <Description>Your AI coding assistant ŌĆö run locally or in the cloud with Ollama. No API keys required. Just you and your code.</Description>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/DevMando/MandoCode</PackageProjectUrl>
